Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:14.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Juiz, it looks like I did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:16.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--You killed?\N--Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:19.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I think we're in the same location as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:25.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I've pinpointed it. Room number 1109.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Could you deal with the aftermath?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:32.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the method to you,\Nbut as elegantly as possible, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:34.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:39.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Noblesse oblige. I pray that\Nyou shall continue to be a savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:54.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(319,398)}Episode 5:\NThis Is No Time to Be Thinking About That...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:01.81,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So before I lost my memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:05.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I was already involved in this thorny game...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:09.72,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If I think of it as having sold\Nmy life to that Mr. Outside dude
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:12.74,Font 1,,0,0,0,,for ten billion yen, that's a major deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:21.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Damn it to hell! This pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Who is this "Mr. Outside," anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:29.17,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I won't be happy until I\Npunch out that stupid jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:35.84,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:39.44,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Don't I get killed by the\N"Supporter" if I throw this out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:45.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Akira Takizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:49.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Why you low down, dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:54.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Who are you? The Supporter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Where's this coming from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:05.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What do you think we've been\Nthrough these past two months?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.14,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You said you were going to take\Nus to a "consumer's paradise,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:10.01,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and then you abandoned us in\Nthe middle of the damn desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:15.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Then some Indian site foreman railed\Nat us for being useless weaklings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:18.49,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and we survived endless hungry, pathetic days
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:22.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,with no money and no idea what was going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.18,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:29.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Wait, did your memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.19,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:40.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Meat buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:45.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm getting married next month,\Nto a girl from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:49.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't know why you sent us to Dubai,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:54.21,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but at the very least,\Nit helped me reenter society.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:57.18,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:01.65,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(232,266)}Sangetsu Bakery
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:11.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(510,152)}Welcome to\NSangetsu Bakery
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:17.11,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you do this when\Nyou're about to give an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:19.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I've just got no eye for things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's fine, I do it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:30.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I modeled these after your self-portrait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:36.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I think they'll probably be\Nrough on you at the interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:38.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but that's when you have to give it your all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.10,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:46.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But if you just can't take it,\Nyou don't have to strain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:47.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:54.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We'll take care of you until you find\Nsomething you really want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:57.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can't cause you any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:06:01.76,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's no trouble. You're family,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:04.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What a thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:08.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, that kindness hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:53.60,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't notice you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:59.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You hardly look like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:02.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess we never saw each\Notherwhile we were job hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:04.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:07.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It feels like I haven't seen you in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:11.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Even though we just went on\Na graduation trip together...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:14.66,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Did you hear about Hirasawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:17.23,Font 1,,0,0,0,,He's deferring his graduation for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:20.97,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Apparently he decided on it\Nwhile we were in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:26.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh. I've had my suspicions since he\Nsaid he wouldn't go on the trip, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.64,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:31.21,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We started our club with the idea of\Neventually turning it into a business,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:33.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,so I understand how he feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:37.49,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But it's the kind of choice you\Ncan't make if your family's not rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:40.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,He's always down on himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:42.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,saying things like, "Our generation\Nare NEETs at heart," you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:45.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But I think he could make a good\Nstab at life in the workforce.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:48.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You know, Hirasawa actually\Nhas six tentative job offers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,He just hasn't said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:54.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But even a guy like that can\Nend up 30 or 40 years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:58.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,griping about the society he couldn't commit to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:02.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't want Hirasawa to turn out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.35,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.58,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I think you're right, Osugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:16.52,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Saki, do you have some time\Nafter your interview today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:17.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:21.23,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, want to eat together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:24.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,A combined celebration of\Ngraduating and finding jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:27.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We're dressed up, after all,\Nso let's splurge a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:31.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I think I'll wrap up before 2:00,\Nso I'll come pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:33.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:34.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:43.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Congratulations. So you've\Nofficially remembered the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:45.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I haven't actually remembered them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:49.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And this "save Japan" thing is just too vague!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:54.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So, I've been wondering exactly\Nhow possible that really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:09:00.23,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well...Like, there can't be that\Nmany people you'd give a phone to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:04.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,that was capable of anything\Nup to ten billion, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:06.77,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Out of all Japan, it'd be the\NPrime Minister or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:11.58,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Personally, I get the feeling only\Nthe real elites could pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:17.45,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So I've been wondering if we could\Nmake the Prime Minister cry uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:23.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Lucky you, you've got an easy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:25.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--Accepted.\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:29.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Noblesse oblige. Please wait in front of the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:31.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I pray you shall be a savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:39.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,These documents suggest that the\Nmissiles used on Careless Monday
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:42.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs12\pos(318,57)}Lower House Committee on Audit\Nand Oversight of Administration
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:42.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs12\pos(423,303)}Broadcast from Lower House Committee Room 1
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:44.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,may have been those newly deployed\Nby the Maritime Self-Defense Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:46.65,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs12\pos(316,61)}Lower House Committee on Audit\Nand Oversight of Administration
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:46.65,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs12\pos(417,291)}People's Representative Party,\NSewa Policy Research Group\NOsamu Yamamoto
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:47.11,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Mr. Prime Minister, isn't it true that you knew
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:50.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,the missiles which hit our major\Ncities were MSDF cruise missiles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:56.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs17\pos(126,112)}Lower House Committee on Audit and\NOversight of Administration
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:56.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(284,419)}People's Representative Party,\NSewa Policy Research Group\NOsamu Yamamoto
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:53.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And we've also received info\Nthat the terrorists who caused this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:56.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,are part of an organization\Ncalling itself "Selecao."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:10:03.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(512,55)}"Relay"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:03.23,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The Prime Minister has the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:09.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--Uncle.\N--We can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:10.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:16.74,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:20.98,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, I get what you're capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:23.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:24.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,"Saki Morimi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:30.76,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap! I never read that\Nmessage from yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:35.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs17\pos(314,321)}[I went home this\Nmorning without\Nsaying anything,\Nbut did something happen to you?!\NI hope your memories\Njust came back, but I\Ngot a little worried,\Nso i'm texting you.]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:33.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,"I went home this morning\Nwithout saying anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:35.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but did something happen to you?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:37.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I made her worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.21,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Takizawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,"Sorry I couldn't make it to the late show.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:56.58,Font 1,,0,0,0,,My memories aren't coming back,\Nbut I'm doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:11:02.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Say, how about we meet up now?\NThere's something I want to ask you."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:04.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:10.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,She's not responding... I wonder if she's angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:13.53,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll go apologize in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:17.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Juiz, about that girl I was with yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.10,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:32.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Did you see that Diet broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:36.71,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I hear just saying "Uncle" sent\Nhis approval ratings up 10%.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:43.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs20\pos(306,171)}Selecao Activity History
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:43.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs20\pos(316,275)}[Make the Prime\NMinister say "Uncle"]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:43.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs20\pos(333,361)}[Metro Expt. Rt.5\N(Ikebukuro) - Bijoki\NToll Gate]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:43.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So you can get that for 60 yen, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:45.76,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs20\pos(323,318)}Selecao Activity History\N[Update to No. 9's Log]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs20\pos(295,174)}Selecao Activity History
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs20\pos(309,286)}[Find the girl he was\Nwith yesterday]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs20\pos(318,355)}[Make the Prime\NMinister say "Uncle"]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:55.57,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Juiz, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:04.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If you want to be professional\Nmodels, just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:07.81,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You'll have an easier time of it\Nif you practice moderation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:21.44,Font 1,,0,0,0,,My, Number 9 has really started\Nchanging his approach since his return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.84,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Did anyone watch the Diet broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:31.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder how Number 1 will respond to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:33.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,A realist and a romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:38.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of taking\Neither side, but as for cuteness...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:45.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. Do I have any plans for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:52.17,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I may suddenly disappear,\Nso make sure not to lose sight of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.53,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:57.13,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You see, I have a feeling I'll do it again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You were pretty lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,As a survivor of that incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:09.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,how do you see the latest missile terrorism?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:11.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear your honest opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:13.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:19.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Young people welcomed Careless\NMonday pretty warmly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:23.10,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, up until now there were no casualties,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:26.60,Font 1,,0,0,0,,so that kind of rash opinion was possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:31.01,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But there were victims of this recent incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:32.71,Font 1,,0,0,0,,so I have the utmost sympathy for...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:39.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I see, so you're more like\Nthe crowd than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.58,Font 1,,0,0,0,,See, I wanted to hear a frank opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:45.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,from one of the young people\Nwho will shoulder society's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:47.88,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Not a conformist "sound opinion."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:53.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But anyway, I'm glad you made it through safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:56.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Where there's life, there's hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:14:01.64,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, since you came all the way here,\Nhow about an early lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:04.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Our cafeteria is quite well-regarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:11.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs24\pos(77,47)}Meeting Room 13
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:05.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:17.41,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This is weird... Am I in the wrong place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:32.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:35.46,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No, it's okay. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:38.57,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Did you see the beef bowl girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:43.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! It's been a while since\Nthe boss last pulled that trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:46.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Tell me about it. But you know,\Nthe boss may be the bad guy here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:49.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but that girl was super dense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:52.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If she'd caught on after being\Nleft alone there for almost an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:55.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,she wouldn't have had a\Nbeef bowl dumped on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:58.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if she'd gotten a clue...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:01.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,More like, no way she'd land\Na job in this day and age
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:04.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,after vacationing right up until\Nthe day before the interview!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't it naive to think that\Nyou can get a job these days
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:07.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,just on the strength of your connections?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:17.17,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(416,138)}Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:23.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I thought that was going too far,\Nbut you know, she's got talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hello, Sangetsu Bakery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:35.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yes. Oh, thank you for all\Nyou've done for my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:39.49,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Oh, yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:43.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:49.64,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll pass on the message.\NThank you for calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:52.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yes. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:58.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(297,301)}Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:16.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wanted to apologize for\Nthe day before yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:18.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and there's something I'd like\Nyou to tell me, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.77,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So I came in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Saki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:07.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I guess it's only natural they'd reject me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:11.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I thought if I sincerely apologized\Nfor missing the first interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:15.33,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I could work things out, and I\Nthought I'd gotten that chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:17.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But reality wasn't so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:23.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But you know, I don't think they\Nhad to dump a beef bowl on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:29.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was tough to reject me\Nbecause of Ryosuke, but we're adults,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:32.35,Font 1,,0,0,0,,so if they thought they were such\Nbetter members of society than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:34.41,Font 1,,0,0,0,,they could've come out and said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:40.19,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The truth is, there was a\Ncompany I wanted to work at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:44.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But at the interview, I started\Ngetting the feeling that maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:48.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,even though they said, "You young\Npeople are the key players in society,"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:52.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,they really just wanted to\Nuse us for their own gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.87,0:17:55.60,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So I turned down the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:57.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Maybe that was stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:03.18,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But I can't go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:09.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I love my sister and my niece,\Nbut I'm in love with Ryosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:12.52,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I love him so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:15.49,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That's why this is painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:53.33,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Come to my place. I'll take\Nresponsibility for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:56.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hearing you, I've figured out what I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:59.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to force yourself to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:00.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:03.74,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Plus, this country's gone so far around the bend
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:08.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,that somebody's got to do\Nsomething about it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Giving someone ten billion yen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:20.52,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and telling them to save the\Ncountry is just too irresponsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:23.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And that's why the Johnnys are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:28.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to work, Saki.\NThey're the ones it'll hurt in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:31.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So until then, you don't have to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:42.11,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Who are you, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:46.74,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Dunno. But I think I'm about to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:02.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Osugi, please, tell me what this is about already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:06.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of becoming more\Nto you than just a junior in the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.77,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea, Buster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:16.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Everyone eventually becomes a working adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:20.81,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It does no harm to go to a three-star\Nrestaurant or two, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:22.12,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:25.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But why'd you bring me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:41.13,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That cost 80,000 yen...\NNo way am I gonna puke it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:51.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Dammit! What have I been doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:53.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If you've got a boyfriend, tell me so!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:57.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If you had, I would've backed off right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:15.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The night is a seal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:22.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If we mix in some bewilderment, it will end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:34.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If we're in danger of wavering,\Nlet's just abandon our reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:42.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We drown in dreams again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The future stretches on uncertainly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:58.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can still forgive you,\NI can still know the meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:02.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The night exists to be listened to closely
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:09.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can copy that reason, and change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:19.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind cutting off\Nthe future to know your breath
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:25.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind cutting off the future